      "title": "Being-H0.7: A Latent World-Action Model from Egocentric Videos",
      "authors": "Hao Luo, Wanpeng Zhang, Yicheng Feng, Sipeng Zheng, Haiweng Xu, Chaoyi Xu, Ziheng Xi, Yuhui Fu, Zongqing Lu",
      "year": 2026,
